📱 PerFin – Personal Finance App

A modern offline-first personal finance Android app built with Jetpack Compose + MVVM + Room + Hilt.

PerFin focuses on:

💸 Expense tracking
🏦 Multi-account management
🔒 Privacy (no internet usage)
🎯 Smooth UX with animations
🧠 Clean architecture
🚀 Features
💰 Core Finance
Add / Edit / Delete transactions
Supports:
Income
Expense
Transfer (between accounts)
Real-time balance updates
🏦 Accounts
Default account (auto-created)
Multiple account support
Account-wise balance tracking
Safe delete with transaction reassignment
🗂 Categories
Pre-seeded categories
Icons + colors support
Type-based filtering (Income / Expense)
Safe deletion (fallback category)
📊 Dashboard
Total balance (real account-based)
Income / Expense summary
Recent transactions
Donut chart visualization
⚙️ Settings
Dark mode toggle
App lock toggle (ready)
Currency selection
Onboarding state persistence
🎬 UX & Animations
Animated splash screen
Smooth onboarding flow
Mascot-based UI
Modern fintech design
🧠 Tech Stack
Kotlin 2.3+
Jetpack Compose
MVVM Architecture
Room Database (Offline-first)
Hilt (Dependency Injection)
Coroutines + Flow
Navigation Compose
KSP (No kapt)
🧱 Architecture
UI → ViewModel → Repository → DAO → Room DB
Layers:
com.devshiv.perfin
├── data
│   ├── local
│   │   ├── dao
│   │   ├── database
│   │   └── entity
│   ├── repository
│
├── ui
│   ├── screens
│   ├── components
│   ├── navigation
│   ├── theme
│
├── viewmodel
├── di
├── utils
🗄️ Database Design
Entities:
TransactionEntity
AccountEntity
CategoryEntity
SettingsEntity
Key Features:
Foreign key relationships
Transfer handling (dual account updates)
Category linking
Settings persistence
🌱 Database Seeding

Default data is inserted using:

Room Database Callback
Hilt EntryPoint Injection
Safe insert logic (no duplicates)

Includes:

Default account
Default categories
Default settings
📐 UI Highlights
Green fintech theme 🌿
Gold accents ✨
Rounded cards
Gradient backgrounds
Clean typography
📸 Screens
Splash
Onboarding
Home Dashboard
Transactions
Accounts
Settings
Add/Edit Transaction
⚠️ Key Engineering Decisions
Offline-first → no API dependency
Account-based balance (not income-expense derived)
Safe delete logic (accounts & categories)
Seeder + runtime sync (for updates)
Flow-based reactive UI
🔄 Data Flow
Room DB
   ↓ Flow
Repository
   ↓
ViewModel
   ↓
Compose UI
